com.mindfusion.drawing

Class Brush

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.drawing.Brush
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GradientBrush, HatchBrush, RadialGradientBrush, SolidBrush, TextureBrush

    public abstract class Brush
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Externalizable
    A Brush specifies how the interior of an element should be filled. The SolidBrush and GradientBrush classes inherit this abstract class.
